    "Id": "chassisdef_kumazemi_KUZ-F2",
    "Name": "Kumazemi",
    "Details": "The KUZ-F2 represents an alternate development path from the original KUZ-C2, retaining its LRM-15 but replacing the AC/20 with a Gauss Rifle for comparable hitting power without the heat penalty. The head-mounted Machine Gun gives way to an ER Large Laser, while the paired Medium Lasers are replaced by a Large Pulse Laser and a Medium Pulse Laser for greater precision at range. Endo Steel structure and Ferro-Fibrous armor, along with double heat sinks, round out this substantial overhaul of the chassis's original design.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Rugged</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
